    @Requires(classes={com.amazonaws.ClientConfiguration.class,io.micronaut.configuration.aws.AWSClientConfiguration.class}) @Requires(env="ec2") @Requires(property="aws.client.system-manager.parameterstore.enabled",value="true",defaultValue="false")

public class AWSParameterStoreConfiguration
extends io.micronaut.configuration.aws.AWSClientConfiguration
implements Toggleable
